		        This product contains SAR complex raw data (BAQ uncompressed) in the form of contiguous radar range line.
                        Every product starts with pre calibration frames followed by imaging frames and ends with post calibration frames.
                        Pre-calibration frames consist of noise frames followed by replica frames.
                        Post-calibration frames consist of replica frames followed by noise frames.
			Total file size is sum of size of pre-calibration frames, imaging frames and post-calibration frames.
                        Imaging data may be on-board range compressed or not depending on acquisition mode.
                        Missing PRF have been zero padded.
	    </comment>
